{"tid":45223,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"星座撚麻煩入一入嚟","createTime":"2016-12-18T22:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T23:39:03.000Z","uid":17502,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c41452d824a675c83c7cb2758ca8f620e4bb57","tid":45223,"uid":17502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T22:08:57.000Z","msg":"你哋收皮啦好嗎？星乜撚野座？你哋on9架？無腦架？咁撚大個人唔撚知自己咩性格要靠人話返俾你知啊？咁啱同隔離嗰個有幾分相似就好撚有認同感？柒少陣當幫忙啦好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n你哋知唔知醜架，日日俾人鬧都唔識得反省下，仲覺得人哋係盲屌你，你乜乜柒柒都跟撚住呢啲所謂嘅標準，同on9港女語錄有乜撚野分別啊？求下你哋係擺脫呢啲on9資訊前唔撚好拍拖啊，咪害撚死你自己，同埋害撚死個男/女仔啊。屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n仲有就係，個世界好撚大架，咪撚乜鳩野都將自己放到咁撚大得唔得啊，唔係好多人想知你啲野架，你唔撚洗乜柒都拎出嚟講架柒頭。得閒做下啲有意義嘅野，進修下你自己，會比你睇埋啲on9野更容易溝到女架，講咗啲咩自己參透下。<br />\n<br />\n最後引用返郎郎嘅結尾格式<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">脫星座染污<br />\n聖誕可出pool</span></span>"},{"pid":"6d6bcbe31ccf165a6c3d27d5b4c81a5d719d2200","tid":45223,"uid":4274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T23:12:23.000Z","msg":"開個page反星座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d2bc7d729f82a3ac060698f0a7d554eeeca33d","tid":45223,"uid":12207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T23:18:17.000Z","msg":"樓主威威"},{"pid":"e3545c9f1c0d057550ea92eb23571f6381a538a0","tid":45223,"uid":66512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T23:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845297d2c879f0d3cf29fcdaa4b91b8eb8813127","tid":45223,"uid":40737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T23:36:03.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball"},{"pid":"00d2dc43b0a64b27d60694cd98c2511d1a708199","tid":45223,"uid":8990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T23:36:48.000Z","msg":"支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\